**To create an FPGA image**

The following ``create-fpga-image`` example creates an AFI from the specified tarball in S3. ::

    aws ec2 create-fpga-image \
        --name my-afi \
        --input-storage-location Bucket=my-bucket,Key=my-afi.tar

Output::

    {
        "FpgaImageId": "afi-0abcdef1234567890",
        "FpgaImageGlobalId": "agfi-0abcdef1234567890"
    }
